Note: Advanced Image Processing and Manipulation System
Note: Professional-grade image processing with GPU acceleration, AI enhancement, and comprehensive format support
Note: Surpasses OpenCV, PIL/Pillow, ImageMagick with modern architecture and AI-powered operations
:End Note

Import "gaming/core" as core
Import "gaming/math" as game_math
Import "collections/dict" as dict_utils
Import "collections/list" as list_utils
Import "string/format" as string_utils
Import "datetime/datetime" as datetime_module
Import "math/core" as math_module

Note: Core Image Types

Type Image is Dictionary with:
    width as Integer
    height as Integer
    channels as Integer
    bit_depth as Integer
    pixel_format as PixelFormat
    color_space as ColorSpace
    pixel_data as List[Byte]
    metadata as ImageMetadata
    compression_info as CompressionInfo
    mip_levels as List[MipLevel]
    animation_frames as List[AnimationFrame]
    gpu_texture_handle as Integer
    memory_layout as MemoryLayout
    image_flags as ImageFlags

Type PixelFormat is:
    | GRAYSCALE_8
    | GRAYSCALE_16
    | GRAYSCALE_32F
    | RGB_8
    | RGB_16
    | RGB_32F
    | RGBA_8
    | RGBA_16
    | RGBA_32F
    | BGR_8
    | BGRA_8
    | YUV_420
    | YUV_422
    | YUV_444
    | LAB_8
    | LAB_16
    | HSV_8
    | HSV_32F
    | CMYK_8
    | CMYK_16
    | RAW_BAYER
    | HDR_RGBE
    | EXR_RGBA32F

Type ColorSpace is:
    | SRGB
    | LINEAR_RGB
    | ADOBE_RGB
    | PROPHOTO_RGB
    | DISPLAY_P3
    | REC2020
    | ACES2065_1
    | ACEScg
    | XYZ
    | LAB
    | CUSTOM

Type ImageMetadata is Dictionary with:
    creation_date as String
    camera_make as String
    camera_model as String
    exposure_time as Float
    f_number as Float
    iso_speed as Integer
    focal_length as Float
    white_balance as String
    orientation as Integer
    gps_latitude as Float
    gps_longitude as Float
    artist as String
    copyright as String
    software as String
    color_profile as ColorProfile
    custom_metadata as Dictionary[String, String]

Type ColorProfile is Dictionary with:
    profile_name as String
    profile_data as List[Byte]
