Process calculate_histogram with image as Image:
    Let processor be create_image_processor with backend as CPU_SIMD
    Return compute_image_histogram with processor as processor and image as image

Process calculate_image_statistics with image as Image:
    Let processor be create_image_processor with backend as CPU_SIMD
    Return compute_image_statistics with processor as processor and image as image

Type ImageHistogram is Dictionary with:
    red_histogram as List[Integer]
    green_histogram as List[Integer]
    blue_histogram as List[Integer]
    luminance_histogram as List[Integer]
    bin_count as Integer
    total_pixels as Integer

